license: CC-BY-4.0
abstract: >-
  For a married-filing-jointly household with $200,000 taxable income, the home
  value at which Texas property tax erases the savings from Texas having no
  state income tax, by origin state (California, New York, Illinois, Florida,
  Washington). Modeled at 1.40%, 1.80%, and 2.00% Texas effective
  owner-occupied property-tax rates. Sources: Tax Foundation 2024 effective
  property-tax rates; 2025 state income-tax brackets.
